{"type": "article", "id": 1265, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2014-06-25T13:44:08Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [{"id": 1130, "name": "手表"}, {"id": 1326, "name": "茶壶"}, {"id": 1327, "name": "雨伞"}, {"id": 1328, "name": "灯"}], "category": 17, "column": null, "author": 11, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071134537t0r93RcuZ8kfLbB.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n\t<strong>1. </strong><strong>Picto by </strong><strong>Steen Georg Christensen and Erling Andersen</strong> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n\t丹麦设计师 Steen Georg Christensen 和 Erling Andersen 设计的 Picto 手表推出了夏季的四种颜色，它的极简设计和特殊的机械结构为它在纽约的 MOMA 的陈列里赢得一席之位。它的售价在 115.83 英镑，购买可点击<a href=\"http://www.dezeenwatchstore.com/shop/picto-dusty-blue-dark-brown/\" target=\"_blank\">这里</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113444jrS7WMO51V4vRAhI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113445qi2bAd40T3gOGEFN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"><strong>2. </strong><strong>Handbag by John Edwards of Florian London, UK</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n\t上周在纽约举行的独立品牌包设计师大奖颁奖中，John Edwards 凭借这款天蓝色的皮包获得了最佳设计和最受欢迎奖。\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071134460KOIR4HjMfLoGSwd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6359375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n\t<strong>3. Keep Light by Kaschikasch</strong> \r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n\t无论你是独居，还是有人在家里牵挂着你，深夜回到家，一盏进门的小灯都能在安静的房间里点燃一丝温暖。这盏入门小灯外观简单，却设计贴心。它半遮掩的设计过滤了刺眼的灯光，而下半部弧形的空间正好能放下钥匙和零钱。有了这盏照明的廊灯，你疲惫地回到家后也不用担心抹黑找路，第二天早晨也不会翻箱倒柜地去找昨晚随手一放的钥匙了。\r\n</div>\r\n<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113446DZALNb90hHQ5dYu4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75238095\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113447dXtTbO0lYfmhayCi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6609375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113447L9P2iKBlHSFIdhCV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n\t<strong>4. Lambskin for teapot by Hlutagerðin </strong> \r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n\t冰岛设计工作室 Hlutagerðin 将羊皮包在了茶壶外面用来隔热和保温。古时候，冰岛人会把这种羊皮大量运用在铠甲上，它能起到保暖和保护的作用。这种传统的工艺逐渐被人们遗忘，但冰岛设计师 Elín Bríta 却把它们用在了我们常见的茶壶上，让人们从生活的细节里去品味一些来自远古的冰岛文化。\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113448IZ4ilyfCYBx3LgbA.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66714286\" data-format=\"png\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113448YsgWITOFMzP5BmpC.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66714286\" data-format=\"png\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113449kWfPjhiqYzOCJ9yN.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"png\"><br>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n\t<strong>5. Umbrella by Masaru Suzuki</strong> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n\t下雨天阴沉的天气和湿哒哒的路面容易让人跟着树梢上的枝叶一样垂下了头，如果没有灿烂的阳光，心情难免阴雨。但如果有把色彩斑斓的伞，情况可能大不相同。这些颜色缤纷的伞都是由 Masaru Suzuki 设计的，上周刚在东京结束的伞展是她举办的第三次伞展。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113450pYCscFSX49QZw0Tg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071134500dkaXxrYKInELusm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113451dDITWU5el2uRG61h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5078125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113451lIjq7C3o98fsSHRX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071134526LX4S2aCbcpZquVE.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"png\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113453KFH6iMPEeVDvdgty.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}